name: SchoolQuiz
tagline: SchoolQuizApp is an evaluation quiz for elementary school student for grade 6-7-8.
body:
### Welcome to GitHub Pages.
This is a quiz application using Modified / Hacked SlickQuiz.
Note: The questions of all quiz are based on curriculum of standard 6-7-8 at Gujarat Government Schools.
